---
// Blind Spot Story - Minimal Card Layout
---

<section class="py-20 px-4 bg-gradient-to-b from-background to-background/95">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6">
        Water as the defining <span class="text-primary">Critical Resource</span> of the 21st Century
      </h2>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <!-- Intro Card -->
      <div class="bg-card/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-border/50 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg">
        <blockquote class="text-xl text-foreground/90 italic mb-6">
          "The Water Foundation is set up to tackle a core blind spot of humankind: <span class="font-bold text-primary">WATER</span>"
        </blockquote>
        <p class="text-foreground/80">
          The unrecognised consequences of current and future water availability and access.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Blind Spot Impact -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-6">Due to the blind spot</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <!-- Impact Item -->
          <div class="bg-card/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-border/50 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-foreground mb-2">Enormous Financing Mismatch</h4>
            <p class="text-foreground/80 text-sm">90% of climate adaptation needs are water-based, yet less than 5% of climate finance is directed toward water.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Impact Item -->
          <div class="bg-card/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-border/50 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-foreground mb-2">Severe Resilience Gap</h4>
            <p class="text-foreground/80 text-sm">Many governments and organisations have a wide-open weak spot in their water strategies and implementation.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Impact Item -->
          <div class="bg-card/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-border/50 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-foreground mb-2">Large Asset Neglect</h4>
            <p class="text-foreground/80 text-sm">Water assets are underpriced, fragmented, and underprotected.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Impact Item -->
          <div class="bg-card/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-border/50 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-foreground mb-2">Critical Systemic Fallout</h4>
            <p class="text-foreground/80 text-sm">Water issues will have deep social, political, and ethical consequences.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-foreground/80 mb-6">
          The Water Foundation is stepping up to fill this gap at a systems level, utilizing systems level & first principles thinking.
        </p>
        <a href="/about" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors">
          Learn About Our Approach
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
